#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an6.98"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.98:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.98:0.2"
msgid "10. Ānisaṃsavagga "
msgstr "10. Benefit "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.98:0.3"
msgid "98. Aniccasutta "
msgstr "98. Impermanence "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an6.98:1.1"
msgid "“‘So vata, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kañci saṅkhāraṃ niccato samanupassanto anulomikāya khantiyā samannāgato bhavissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, it’s totally impossible for a mendicant who regards any condition as permanent to accept views that agree with the teaching. "

msgctxt "an6.98:1.2"
msgid "‘Anulomikāya khantiyā asamannāgato sammattaniyāmaṃ okkamissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "Without accepting views that agree with the teaching, it’s impossible to enter the sure path with regards to skillful qualities. "

#. VAR: arahattaṃ → arahattaphalaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an6.98:1.3"
msgid "‘Sammattaniyāmaṃ anokkamamāno sotāpattiphalaṃ vā sakadāgāmiphalaṃ vā anāgāmiphalaṃ vā arahattaṃ vā sacchikarissatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "Without entering the sure path, it’s impossible to realize the fruit of stream-entry, once-return, non-return, or perfection. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.442, sc2
#. VAR: sabbasaṅkhāre → sabbasaṅkhāraṃ (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an6.98:2.1"
msgid "‘So vata, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sabbasaṅkhāre aniccato samanupassanto anulomikāya khantiyā samannāgato bhavissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "It’s totally possible for a mendicant who regards all conditions as impermanent to accept views that agree with the teaching. "

msgctxt "an6.98:2.2"
msgid "‘Anulomikāya khantiyā samannāgato sammattaniyāmaṃ okkamissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "Having accepted views that agree with the teaching, it’s possible to enter the sure path. "

msgctxt "an6.98:2.3"
msgid "‘Sammattaniyāmaṃ okkamamāno sotāpattiphalaṃ vā sakadāgāmiphalaṃ vā anāgāmiphalaṃ vā arahattaṃ vā sacchikarissatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti. "
msgstr "Having entered the sure path, it’s possible to realize the fruit of stream-entry, once-return, non-return, or perfection.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.98:2.4"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

